quran[18]{c,v,t,f}:
  26,139,"Nítorí náà, wọ́n pè é ní òpùrọ́. A sì pa wọ́n run. Dájúdájú àmì wà nínú ìyẹn. Ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ wọn ni kò sì jẹ́ onígbàgbọ́ òdodo."
  26,140,"Dájúdájú Olúwa rẹ, Òun mà ni Alágbára, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run."
  26,141,"Àwọn ìran Thamūd pe àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ ní òpùrọ́."
  28,85,"Dájúdájú Ẹni tí Ó ṣe al-Ƙur’ān ní ọ̀ran-anyàn fún ọ (láti mú un lò àti láti pèpè sí i), Ó sì máa dá ọ padà sí ibùpadàsí kan (nínú Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra). Sọ pé: “Olúwa mi nímọ̀ jùlọ nípa ẹni tí ó mú ìmọ̀nà wá àti ta ni ó wà nínú ìṣìnà pọ́nńbélé.”"
  28,86,"Ìwọ kò sì retí pé A óò sọ tírà al-Ƙur’ān kalẹ̀ fún ọ (tẹ́lẹ̀), àmọ́ ó jẹ́ ìkẹ́ kan láti ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa rẹ. Nítorí náà, o ò gbọdọ̀ jẹ́ olùrànlọ́wọ́ fún àwọn aláìgbàgbọ́."
  28,87,"Má ṣe jẹ́ kí wọ́n ṣẹ́ ọ lórí kúrò níbi àwọn āyah Allāhu lẹ́yìn ìgbà tí A ti sọ̀ ọ́ kalẹ̀ fún ọ. Pèpè sí ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa rẹ. Ìwọ kò sì gbọ́dọ̀ wà nínú àwọn ọ̀ṣẹbọ."
  29,52,"Sọ pé: “Allāhu tó ní Ẹlẹ́rìí láààrin èmi àti ẹ̀yin. Ó mọ ohunkóhun tó wà nínú àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ilẹ̀. Àwọn tó gba irọ́ (òrìṣà) gbọ́, tí wọ́n sì ṣàì gbàgbọ́ nínú Allāhu; àwọn wọ̀nyẹn, àwọn ni ẹni òfò."
  29,53,"Wọ́n sì ń kán ọ lójú nípa ìyà! Tí kò bá jẹ́ pé ó ti ní gbèdéke àkókò kan ni, ìyà náà ìbá kúkú dé bá wọn. (Ìyà) ìbá dé bá wọn ní òjijì sẹ́, tí wọn kò sì níí fura."
  29,54,"Wọ́n ń kán ọ lójú nípa ìyà! Dájúdájú iná Jahanamọ kúkú máa yí àwọn aláìgbàgbọ́ po."
  30,31,"(Ẹ jẹ́) olùṣẹ́rí padà sí ọ̀dọ̀ Allāhu (nípa ìronúpìwàdà). Ẹ páyà Rẹ̀. Ẹ kí ìrun. Ẹ má ṣe wà nínú àwọn ọ̀ṣẹbọ."
  30,32,"(Ẹ má ṣe wà) nínú àwọn tó dá ẹ̀sìn wọn sí kélekèle, tí wọ́n sì di ìjọ-ìjọ. Ìjọ kọ̀ọ̀kan sì ń yọ̀ sí ohun tí ó wà lọ́dọ̀ wọn."
  30,33,"Nígbà tí ìnira kan bá fọwọ́ ba ènìyàn, wọn yóò pe Olúwa wọn, tí wọn yóò máa ṣẹ́rí padà sọ́dọ̀ Rẹ̀. Lẹ́yìn náà, nígbà tí (Allāhu) bá fún wọn ní ìkẹ́ kan tọ́ wò láti ọ̀dọ̀ Rẹ̀, nígbà náà ni igun kan nínú wọn yóò máa ṣẹbọ sí Olúwa wọn"
  31,16,"Ọmọ mi, dájúdájú tí ó bá jẹ́ pé òdiwọ̀n èso kardal kan{1} ló wà nínú àpáta, tàbí nínú àwọn sánmọ̀, tàbí nínú ilẹ̀, Allāhu yóò mú un wá. Dájúdájú Allāhu ni Aláàánú, Alámọ̀tán..",footnotes:1:Ìyẹn dúró fún òdíwọ̀n tó kéré gan-an bíi ọmọ-iná igún.
  31,17,"Ọmọ mi, kírun, p’àṣẹ rere, kọ aburú, kí o sì ṣe sùúrù lórí ohun tí ó bá ṣẹlẹ̀ sí ọ. Dájúdájú ìyẹn wà nínú àwọn ìpinnu ọ̀rọ̀ tó pọn dandan."
  31,18,"Má ṣe kọ párìkẹ́ rẹ sí ènìyàn. Má sì ṣe rìn lórí ilẹ̀ pẹ̀lú fáàrí. Dájúdájú Allāhu kò fẹ́ràn gbogbo onígbèéraga, onífáàrí."
  32,1,"’Alif lām mīm. (Allāhu ló mọ ohun tí Ó gbàlérò pẹ̀lú àwọn háràfí náà.){1}.",footnotes:1:Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al Baƙọrah; 2:1.
  32,2,"Ìsọ̀kalẹ̀ Tírà náà, kò sí iyèméjì nínú rẹ̀ (pé ó wá) láti ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa gbogbo ẹ̀dá."
  32,3,"Tàbí wọ́n ń wí pé: “Ó dá àdápa irọ́ rẹ̀ ni.” Rárá o! Òdodo ni láti ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa rẹ nítorí kí o lè fi ṣèkìlọ̀ fún àwọn ènìyàn kan, tí olùkìlọ̀ kan kò wá bá wọn rí ṣíwájú rẹ, nítorí kí wọ́n lè mọ̀nà.{1}.",footnotes:1:Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al-Ƙọsọs; 28:46.